description:
Enjoy in 2K without the livestream blurriness!
Spatial Audio on YouTube is still experimental, especially when processing from VRChat Stereo audio. There's not much documentation on it, but I tried my best! 
Let me know if you can tell the difference~
Huge shout out to Nullrefrepro and VRChat team for help with figuring this out!
